snippet.title: Longplay of Totally Spies! 2: Undercover
snippet.description:
Longplay of Totally Spies! 2: Undercover, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Advance. This game's version was released on Nov. 17th, 2006. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Start
0:00:49 - Arnold The Great
0:14:06 - Booby Blooms
0:29:05 - Hot Thief
0:43:04 - Espionage On The Farm
0:56:01 - Spies In Space
1:07:49 - End
1:12:29 - Credits

By: Terua
